					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My brain decided to interpret that the last ice cream was actually [REDACTED]-flavored.<br /> Not that it was censored, but that the tub actually tasted like redaction.</p> <p>I'm imagining a combination of black marker, shredded paper, and utter lack of sensory data.<br /> Possibly with a fudge swirl.</p> 
