				<wikidot:authorName>Noelemahc</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2821308</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>But wait, if they're all-powerful reality benders, why do they insist on using Foundation personnel as test subjects?</p> <p>Corollary: Do the subjects retain memories of their deaths? Do they try to resist or they have accepted their fate or they have been&#8230; Educated?<br /> So, is this a reality-bending version of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1733">SCP-1733</a> or of that computer with self-replicating videos whose number I cannot recall?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
