					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-763804#post-1939360</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-763804/scp-1765#post-1939360</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2014 22:09:19 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Francis Willjam</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1394675</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>On another read-through, things I've wondered;</p> <ul> <li>How have MTF teams been lost? Are the entities actively hostile toward them?</li> <li>Basically an entire lack of foundation theorising about the entities (which I forgave in Meg's Diner, but it seems a bit off here)</li> <li>No real information about the staff inside the area, are they still the same people, are they being forced to do these things, are they trying to escape etc</li> <li>The temporal thing is kind of glossed over, addendum A section B provided 200+ days of footage, is that how much time actually lapsed or not?</li> </ul> <p>I know it's more of a wink to the reader kind of article, and it's written perfectly, but for me it just seems to be another &quot;mythological beings placed into foundation universe&quot; but this time not enough of a foundation take on it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
