					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-763804#post-1937775</guid>
				<title>General Commentary</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-763804/scp-1765#post-1937775</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2014 00:01:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Dmatix</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1366080</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I always enjoy writing mythology-based SCPs, and this one was no different in that regard. I've also been wanting to do another Keter SCP for a while now, and I think that this particular allusion lends itself well to both. The easter eggs in this SCP are fewer than what I usually do because I felt it would be too distracting. I have to say, the tests were a lot of fun to write.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
